				<li><strong>Feat:</strong> Crafter</li>
				<li><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> Investigation, Persuasion</li>
				<li><strong>Tool Proficiency:</strong> Choose one kind of Artisan Tool</li>
				<li><strong>Equipment:</strong> Choose A or B: (A) Artisan's Tool (same above), 2 Pouches, Travelers's Clothes, 32GP; or (B) 50GP.</li>
